<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1241753-is-mother-courage-and-her-children-is-anti">is mother courage and her children is anti war play or not if yes then tell those aspects if not then also give reason about it i want answer in detail ?????</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1241753'><a id="like_count_community_question_1241753" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1241753?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F85679.Mother_Courage_and_Her_Children">like</a></span>

