<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1241753-is-mother-courage-and-her-children-is-anti">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1241753-is-mother-courage-and-her-children-is-anti">Add your answer</a>
</li>
