<span id="freeTextContainer11190659144512982521">A book I had to read for school, but by the time I realized it was due on Monday, it was Sunday evening and I couldn&apos;t find the book anywhere so I found it in on the Internet in English. Interesting experience.<br/><br/>The book itself was also engaging because of its simple yet interesting writing. I especially liked the inserted songs, so different from the typical choir in the famed antique works.</span>
