          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Bettie</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/900147-laura?shelf=german-literature">german-literature</a>, 
