<span id="freeTextContainer7337834938901363259">Weird.<br/><br/>It took me an unreasonably long amount of time to finish this considering its so short. Some interesting stuff but frustratingly unbrechtian, not to mention lacking in any sort of propulsion.<br/><br/>It&apos;s interesting tho and I don&apos;t hate it.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText7337834938901363259" style="display:none">Weird.<br /><br />It took me an unreasonably long amount of time to finish this considering its so short. Some interesting stuff but frustratingly unbrechtian, not to mention lacking in any sort of propulsion.<br /><br />It's interesting tho and I don't hate it.<br /></span>
